  1836                                  ;
  1837                                  ; A value of FFFF is 65536 samples. Running at 44.1Khz, that's just about
  1838                                  ; 1.5 seconds of sample time. FFFF * 32bits is 1FFFFh bytes or 128k of data.
  1839                                  ;
